{"_path":"/maps/_programming/dx","_dir":"_programming","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Developer Experience（DX）","description":"开发者体验（Developer Experience，DX）是指开发者在使用产品、工具、框架等过程中的感受和体验。它是用户体验（User Experience，UX）的一个子集，专注于开发者的需求和体验。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"developer-exception-engineering"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"link","props":{"type":"h5","to":"https://mgear-file.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/Developer%20Exception%20Engineering.html","source":"https://www.swyx.io/developer-exception/"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"《Developer Exception Engineering》"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SWYX 认为社区在过去讨论 Developer Experience 的角度稍稍狭隘了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"能效提升"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：提高代码效率、自动化、代码生成器、开箱即用。.."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"富文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：起步文档、代码示例、可交互示例、API 清单、最佳实践、可搜索。.."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开发者工具"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：脚手架、编辑器插件、代码片段、代码展示、版本控制。.."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这些东西对开发者来说时“友好的”，但是也很“简单”。也许是时候主动跳出站在开发者的角度思考 DX 的舒适区，开始转向终端用户。也许可以尝试保证这些东西："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"服务可用"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：产品数据页面和报错页面会说谎吗？..."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"反馈有效"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：是否及时有效的解决了客户反馈？..."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"功能完整"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：是否发布了不完整甚至需要返工的功能？..."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"产品路线完整"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：对产品路线的规划是否清晰合理？..."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"计价合理"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：用户会对你的报价产生疑惑么，它是否是可计算和比较的？..."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"兼容性"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：废弃的 API 是否合理？..."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"报错优雅"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：出错后是否可调试？..."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"访问控制"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：客户有审计日志或访问控制的权力吗？..."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"正如面对漏水的桶下雨解决不了问题，如果只是一直站在开发者的角度思考 DX，对解决品牌满意度下降、客户流失这些“异常”没有办法带来帮助。此外，根据康威定律，一个不合理的 DX 会反映出公司的组织架构的不合理之处，这值得引起注意。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"The Experience of Developer | https://www.swyx.io/developer-exception/","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20210917170405.png"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_programming:dx.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_programming/dx.md","_stem":"6.maps/_programming/dx","_extension":"md"}